					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The Vs. System Zapper is a serial device that behaves like a standard controller where Up is always pressed, Left is 1 when light and 0 when dark, and Right is the trigger.<br /><br />Source: <a href="https://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Zapper" class="postlink">&quot;Zapper&quot; on the wiki</a></div>

